summary:
I'm part off the Sales Operations team who are responsible for the daily operational tasks (  like taking care of new orders, sharing the right info about shipments, working out RMA's etc. ) for all our Business Partners worldwide, except Asia and North America. 

I am also responsible for the (automatic) invoicing of all our online services towards all our partners worldwide. This was set up in 2020.

Next to this I'm also Partner Manager for some South-Eastern European Business Partners which I help in the best possible way!
